rating_comment: Amazing experience. Words can’t express the satisfaction. Awesome place. Awesome hospitality. Everything is awesome. For me it’s always going to be my first choice whenever I am in Siliguri. Really home away from home and tasty home food is icing on cake!! Don’t miss to explore!

Anyone planning to Host should actually consult her before starting. She is a perfect host. A very humble and friendly person. I had a lovely stay, it felt like I was staying at my own home. Very clean and peaceful stay. She is a great cook and I will definitely miss the homely and delicious home cooked meals. One should not think before booking Maria Ann's Home! Given a chance I'll definitely stay again and recommend anyone for her place. Thanks for the lovely hospitality!
